&lt;li&gt;Experienced in full-lifecycle recruiting, with 2-5 years either in-house or in a staffing agency environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A sourcing master in your ability to identify where top talent lives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Autonomous with a demonstrated ability to work independently and simultaneously on multiple positions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional at selling value proposition, negotiating and closing great candidates&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at operating with a sense of urgency in all stages of the recruiting cycle&lt;/li&gt;
