&lt;p&gt;The IT Operations - SaaS team is responsible for the SaaS landscape that Datadog employees around the world use on a daily basis to successfully do their jobs. As a SaaS Administrator 2 for the Enterprise IT Operations - SaaS team, you will maintain and improve SaaS services at Datadog such as Google Workspace, Slack, Zoom and hundreds of other SaaS applications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;At Datadog, we place value in our office culture - the relationships and collaboration it builds and the creativity it brings to the table. We operate as a hybrid workplace to ensure our Datadogs can create a work-life harmony that best fits them.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
